About this item

  • 3 Temperature adjustable Setting: Coffee mug warmer will keep your coffee at a good drinking temperature, keeping beverage up to 149 /65 , 131 /55 , 113 /45 by touching the ON/OFF Switch. You can enjoy your hot coffee any time
  • 8 Hour Auto Shut-Off Timer: This coffee warmer for desk auto shut off has 4 timing functions: 2 H/4 H/6 H/8 H. The default setting of warmer is 8 hours automatic shut off. Don't worry about forgetting to close it, there is no safety hazard
  • Compatible with Most Cups: 4.5 Inches large heating plate, oversized base to fit for most mugs (NOT suitable for plastic cups and double insulation mugs) , glass cups, stainless steel cups and baby bottles, and you can even use this cup warmer for desk as a candle warmer to fill your room with fragrance. When using a small sized cup, the silicone rubber ring design on the top of the cup cushion can not only reduce heat dissipation, but also protect your hands from scalding
  • Cute Cat Mug and Warmer Set: Bsigo coffee mug warmer set included with 100% ceramic material cute cat cup 14 oz(400 ML) capacity and little cat paw spoon. Place a kawaii cat lid to cover the mug will also help retain heat. This ceramic mug is designed with special frosted cup bottom for fast heating, always enjoy your hot coffee at any time at office and home. Bring warmth and joy to your love ones and families with Bsigo Warmer and Mug present Set
  • Stylish and Cute design Present: This kitty mug warmer set would also make a wonderful present for any cat lover! Keep beverage warm all day, this mug warmer and cat cup set is a good present for coffee lovers and families. Tea warmer will be your best present choice to show your care to your loved friends on Mother's Day, Christmas, Valentine's Day, Thanksgiving, Birthday or other special occasions

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      Customers say

      Customers find the coffee mug warmer cute, functional, and perfect as a gift. The cup size receives mixed feedback - while some say it's large enough for all mugs, others find it too small. Moreover, the temperature control and build quality get mixed reviews, with some saying it keeps drinks warm while others report it doesn't heat properly, and some units breaking within a month of use. Additionally, opinions on value for money are divided between those who find it worth the price and those who consider it useless.

        5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and functional
        Reviewed in the United States on September 24, 2024
        Verified Purchase
        I've had mine for almost two years with about weekly use for several hours each time. It's also gone through two moves - thoroughly padded - with me with no visible damage.

        I use the warmer on low (blue light) with a steel teapot on the provided coaster.

        The mug is adorable, has a nice weight, and is comfortable to hold. I have larger hands (long fingers, wide palm) so I tend to cup my mugs through the handle with my first three fingers (pinky out for better grip) and this mug makes that easy to do.

        The spoon is nice and it's great for stirring in honey. Love the cat's paw handle

        The cover is great for keeping warmth in, just remember to completely dry after use or it might mold, which would be a shame. The cat head knob is a nice touch to tie everything together.

        All in all, this is a great set with cohesive design and satisfactory functionality. 10/10 would recommend if you like cats and warm drinks. I will certainly buy from this brand again.
